        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-04-02 10:20:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\nI am ok with this. It's just that Liam is also planning to bring 2 sets of models - authorative (with basic pojo structure) & persistence (with JPA implementation). Also the mapping between these 2 sets. In that case, we will not need to maintain 1 more set in policy-models-pap and the corresponding Mapper which this review is bringing in.\nI am ok if we want to bring it in now and delete later.",
        "patchset_number": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "5d014659e0452548f4bd91c9142ac358cfe8e307",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3239,
          "name": "Ram Krishna Verma",
