        "timestamp": "2019-04-02 10:57:30.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\n> Why can't we use \"authorative\" models from models-pdp directly in\n > REST if they are exactly same?\n\nThat would be fine with me, but would require a couple of changes to the REST API: 1) change PdpInstanceDetails to Pdp  2) change Policy to ToscaPolicy",
        "patchset_number": 11
      },
